comments: i focoused on the ending of each word. once id seen they all started the same i associated the end words with words i already knew so that when the picture flashed up i was associating it with a simpler  version of the language. the latter part of the experiment was the hardest as i struggled to distinguish certain letters as it appeared to note what word was being said. in addition the first part where i was learning the words was quite long, and it was harder to remained focused towards the end as it was not overly engaging.
